## Data Mapping

### Map Domain Entities to UI Models at Bottom of ViewModel

```kotlin
// GOOD: Keep mapping at bottom
private fun User.mapToUI() = UserUI(
    id = this.id,
    name = this.name
)

private fun List<User>.mapToUI() = this.map { it.mapToUI() }.toPersistentList()
```

### ❌ Don't expose domain models in UI State
```kotlin
// BAD
data class Data(val users: List<User>) : UiState()

// GOOD
data class Data(val users: PersistentList<UserUI>) : UiState()
```

