## Dependency Injection

### Koin Binding Pattern
In `di/YourFeatureModule.kt`:
```kotlin
val myFeatureModule = module {
    viewModelOf(::MyFeatureViewModel)
    single<MyNavigator> { MyNavigatorImpl() }
}
```

### ViewModel Constructor
All dependencies are resolved via Koin:
```kotlin
class MyFeatureViewModel(
    private val repository: MyRepository,  // From domain
    private val navigator: MyNavigator,     // From coreui
    private val tracking: TrackingRepository // From tracking
) : ViewModel()
```

